com.quinsoft.zeidon.domains

Class GeneratedKeyDomain

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.quinsoft.zeidon.domains.AbstractDomain
      • com.quinsoft.zeidon.domains.GeneratedKeyDomain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Domain

    public class GeneratedKeyDomain
extends AbstractDomain
    This is a domain for storing keys generated by the DB. The domain is constructed in a way that it can hold keys for any DB. Internally the keys are stored as strings and it is up to the DBHandler to convert it to the correct type.
